{{Infobox company | name = Juno Healthcare Staffing | logo = JUNOhealthcareStaffing.gif | logo_size = 160px | type = Private | foundation = 2001 | location = [[New York City]], United States | key_people = Dante Raul Teodoro ([[President (corporate title)|President]]) Nonette Teodoro ([[Chief executive officer|CEO]]) Charmaine Teodoro ([[Senior Vice President]]) industry = [[Health care|Healthcare]], Healthcare Staffing | homepage = [http://www.junohealthcare.com www.junohealthcare.com] }}
'''JUNO Healthcare Staffing'''[http://www.junohealthcare.com] is a [[Employment agency|placement]] service for local and foreign [[healthcare]] professionals on a [[full time]], travel and [[per diem]] assignments to client facilities across the United States. It was founded in 2001 by [[Dante Raul "DR" Teodoro]] in response to the [[nursing shortage]] and rising need for [[healthcare professionals]] in the [[healthcare industry]]. Composed of only three employees in 2001, JUNO has grown into one of the biggest Filipino-owned healthcare staffing agencies in the US. Headquartered in New York, JUNO Healthcare has affiliate offices in different [[US States]] and abroad.
'''JUNO Healthcare Group of Companies''' is composed of JUNO-[[New York City]], JUNO-[[New Jersey]], JUNO-[[Connecticut]], JUNO-[[Los Angeles]] (CA), JUNO-[[San Diego]] (CA), JUNO-[[Arizona]], and JUNO-[[Philippines]].
'''JUNO Investment Management Inc.''' is the [[parent company]] of all JUNO Group of Companies inclusive of JUNO Media Production Creatives, [http://www.junoreview.com Juno Review] and [[Foundation for God’s Glory|Foundation for God's Glory]].
JUNO Healthcare is ranked as one of the Hot 100 List of fastest-growing new businesses in [[United States|America]] as featured by [[Entrepreneur Magazine]] in 2008.<ref>http://www.entrepreneur.com/hot100/details/200886.html Entrepreneur Magazine's Hot 100 Company Rankings</ref> Certified by the [[Joint Commission]], JUNO Healthcare Registry in Los Angeles, California.<ref>http://junohealthcare.com/News08/news_GoldSeal.htm Juno Healthcare Registry, Inc. in Los Angeles, California, receives Gold Seal of Approval from The Joint Commission</ref>
